                        </h2>
                        <div id="faq6" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body text-muted small">
                                @siteName works with a network of <strong>in-house investors</strong> who fund loans directly through our platform. Depending on the terms of your agreement, your repayments may be directed to the investor who backed your loan. This is fully transparent — your loan agreement will clearly outline the funding source and repayment details before you accept any offer. This investor-backed model allows us to offer faster approvals and more competitive rates than traditional banks.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item border-0 rounded-3 shadow-sm mb-2">
